actions.description: Runs python with the data input. Any prints will be returned.
actions.label: remove_duplicate
actions.name: execute_python

parameters.description: The code to run. Can be a file ID from within Shuffle.
parameters.name: code
parameters.value:
import json
list_1 = $json_to_list.message
list_2 = $list_ip.body.ip
combined_list = list(set(json.dumps(item, sort_keys=True) for item in list_1 + list_2))
combined_list = [json.loads(item) for item in combined_list]
json_output = json.dumps(combined_list)
print(json_output)
